    962  f485							; Missile-0 cycle-74 strobe table (must stay within one page).
    963  f485							;   Each entry strobes RESM0; the $1C (NOP abs) swallows the next
    964  f485							;   entry's `sta RESM0`, so only the jumped-to strobe executes, then
    965  f485							;   execution falls through to `sta HMOVE` at cycle ~74.
    966  f485							;-------------------------------------------------------------
    967  f500					      org	$f500
    968  f500				   PosTblM0
